an></strong> if <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">a</span> is a perfect square,    <strong><span>FALSE</span></strong> otherwise.   </p>  </div>    <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 examples" id="refsect1-function.gmp-perfect-square-examples">   <h3 class="title">范例</h3>   <span>    <div class="example" id="example-4084">     <p><strong>Example #1 <span class="function"><strong style="color:#CC7832">gmp_perfect_square()</strong></span> example</strong></p>     <div class="example-contents"> <div class="phpcode" style="border-color:gray;background:#232525"><span><span style="color: #000000"> <span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php<br /></span><span style="color: #FF8000">//&nbsp;3&nbsp;*&nbsp;3,&nbsp;perfect&nbsp;square<br /></span><span style="color: #9876AA">var_dump</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">gmp_perfect_square</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"9"</span><span style="color: #007700">));<br /><br /></span><span style="color: #FF8000">//&nbsp;not&nbsp;a&nbsp;perfect&nbsp;square<br /></span><span style="color: #9876AA">var_dump</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">gmp_perfect_square</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"7"</span><span style="color: #007700">));<br /><br /></span><span style="color: #FF8000">//&nbsp;1234567890&nbsp;*&nbsp;1234567890,&nbsp;perfect&nbsp;square<br /></span><span style="color: #9876AA">var_dump</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">gmp_perfect_square</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"1524157875019052100"</span><span style="color: #007700">));<br /></span><span style="color: #9876AA">?&gt;</span> </span> </span></div>     </div>      <div class="example-contents"><p>以上例程会输出：</p></div>     <div class="example-contents screen" style="bac