/**
*<div id="function.gmp-prob-prime" class="refentry">  <div class="refnamediv">   <h1 class="refname">gmp_prob_prime</h1>   <p class="verinfo">(PHP 4 &gt;= 4.0.4, PHP 5, PHP 7)</p><p class="refpurpose"><span class="refname">gmp_prob_prime</span> &mdash; <span class="dc-title">Check if number is &quot;probably prime&quot;</span></p>   </div>    <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 description" id="refsect1-function.gmp-prob-prime-description">   <h3 class="title">说明</h3>   <div class="methodsynopsis dc-description" style="border:1px gray;padding-left:5px;background:#232525">    <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766">int</span> <span class="methodname" style="color:#CC7832"><strong>gmp_prob_prime</strong></span>     ( <span class="methodparam"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/class.gmp.php" class="type GMP" style="color:#EAB766">GMP</a></span> <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">$a</span></span>    [, <span class="methodparam"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766">int</span> <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">$reps</span><span class="initializer"> = 10</span></span>   ] )</div>    <p class="para rdfs-comment">    The function uses Miller-Rabin&#039;s probabilistic test to check if a number is a prime.   </p>  </div>    <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 parameters" id="refsect1-function.gmp-prob-prime-parameters">   <h3 class="title">参数</h3>   <span>    <dl>            <dt> <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">a</span></dt>       <dd>        <p class="para">        The number being checked as a prime.       </p>       <p class="para">可以是一个 GMP 数据 <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><span class="type resouce" style="color:#EAB766">resouce</span></span>，或一个可以转换为数值的字符串。</p>       </dd>                 <dt> <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">reps</span></dt>       <dd>        <p class="para">        Reasonable values        of <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">reps</span> vary from 5 to 10 (default being        10); a higher value lowers the probability for a non-prime to        pass as a &quot;probable&quot; prime.       </p>       <p class="para">可以是一个 GMP 数据 <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><span class="type resouce" style="color:#EAB766">resouce</span></span>，或一个可以转换为数值的字符串。</p>       </dd>          </dl>    </span>  </div>    <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-function.gmp-prob-prime-returnvalues">   <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>   <p class="para">    If this function returns 0, <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">a</span> is    definitely not prime. If it returns 1, then    <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">a</span> is &quot;probably&quot; prime.  If it returns 2,    then <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">a</span> is surely prime.    </p>  </div>    <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 examples" id="refsect1-function.gmp-prob-prime-examples">   <h3 class="title">范例</h3>   <span>    <div class="example" id="example-4088">     <p><strong>Example #1 <span class="function"><strong style="color:#CC7832">gmp_prob_prime()</strong></span> example</strong></p>     <div class="example-contents"> <div class="phpcode" style="border-color:gray;background:#232525"><span><span style="color: #000000"> <span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php<br /></span><span style="color: #FF8000">//&nbsp;definitely&nbsp;not&nbsp;a&nbsp;prime<br /></span><span style="color: #007700">echo&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">gmp_prob_prime</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"6"</span><span style="color: #007700">)&nbsp;.&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"\n"</span>