">start</span></dt>       <dd>        <p class="para">        The starting bit.       </p>      </dd>          </dl>    </span>  </div>    <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-function.gmp-scan1-returnvalues">   <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>   <p class="para">    Returns the index of the found bit, as an <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.integer.php" class="type integer" style="color:#EAB766">integer</a></span>.    If no set bit is found, -1 is returned.   </p>  </div>    <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 examples" id="refsect1-function.gmp-scan1-examples">   <h3 class="title">范例</h3>   <span>    <div class="example" id="example-4094">     <p><strong>Example #1 <span class="function"><strong style="color:#CC7832">gmp_scan1()</strong></span> example</strong></p>     <div class="example-contents"> <div class="phpcode" style="border-color:gray;background:#232525"><span><span style="color: #000000"> <span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php<br /></span><span style="color: #FF8000">//&nbsp;"1"&nbsp;bit&nbsp;is&nbsp;found&nbsp;at&nbsp;position&nbsp;3.&nbsp;index&nbsp;starts&nbsp;at&nbsp;0<br /></span><span style="color: #9876AA">$s1&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #007700">=&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">gmp_init</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"01000"</span><span style="color: #007700">,&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">2</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br />echo&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">gmp_scan1</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$s1</span><span style="color: #007700">,&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">0</span><span style="color: #007700">)&nbsp;.&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"\n"</span><span style="color: #007700">;